{"title":"Redshift’s New ShockStop Stems in 50 and 70 mm Lengths","link":"https://theradavist.com/redshifts-shockstop-stem-50-70-mm/","date":1723557625000,"content":"<p><img width=\"2120\" height=\"1414\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?fit=1200,1414&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?w=2120&amp;quality=75 2120w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-70mm-ShockStop-Stem-on-bike.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://theradavist.com/search/Redshift/\" target=\"_blank\">Redshift</a> just announced two new ShockStop Stems, available in 55 mm and 70 mm lengths ($189.99) for progressive gravel bikes. With gravel bikes adopting <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/kona-ouroborus-supreme-review/\" target=\"_blank\">longer top tubes and slacker head angles</a> like their mountain bike kin, they require shorter stems. This includes riders in need of a shorter stem to achieve a proper bike fit as well.<span></span></p>\n<p><img width=\"1660\" height=\"1107\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-50-70mm-ShockStop-Stem.jpg?fit=1200,1107&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-50-70mm-ShockStop-Stem.jpg?w=1660&amp;quality=75 1660w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-50-70mm-ShockStop-Stem.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-50-70mm-ShockStop-Stem.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/08/Redshift-Sports-50-70mm-ShockStop-Stem.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Specs:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Effective Suspension Travel: Up to 20 mm</li>\n<li>Designed for Modern Geometry</li>\n<li> Extremely Light: 55 mm stem is only 196 grams</li>\n<li>Adjustable Preload: Includes swappable elastomers to fine-tune your riding style</li>\n<li>Ultra wide range of lengths:</li>\n<li>New design for 55 mm and 70 mm lengths</li>\n<li>Existing design: 80 mm, 90 mm, 100 mm, 110 mm, 120 mm</li>\n<li>Retail price is $189.99 USD</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://redshiftsports.com/collections/suspension-stems\" target=\"_blank\">Redshift</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/redshifts-shockstop-stem-50-70-mm/\">Redshift’s New ShockStop Stems in 50 and 70 mm Lengths</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"1fb2b23afa85bb2b74e47acdf8e8b653aa5a3f6057b883b338492274dd6a6152","category":"Cycling"}